well.. you could make a script that iterates through every single Object in the game, removing (or setting the boolean to false) 'take' and 'look' at the start of the game... laughs:

foreach (x, AllObjects()) {
-&gt; list remove (x.displayverbs, &quot;take&quot;)
-&gt; list remove (x.displayverbs, &quot;look&quot;)
}
